  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939630/extras/7e6d7e5e1c88718de57884ddfd835602.webp?t=1741582473\" width=608 height=32 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939630/extras/c143ae52872419811fa2d8883f11f991.poster.avif?t=1741582473\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939630/extras/c143ae52872419811fa2d8883f11f991.webm?t=1741582473\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939630/extras/c143ae52872419811fa2d8883f11f991.mp4?t=1741582473\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About this game</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> No jump button<br></li><li> Auto move left and right: The player chooses left and right for Proxy to auto-move in that direction<br></li><li> Auto attack: when an enemy is in range, the proxy will auto attack the enemy, the player can stop the attack by toggle<br></li><li> Active and passive skills: using active skills with QWER<br></li><li> Different weapons: there are many weapons giving different stats and sometimes have special skill in it<br></li><li> Rogue-like, the player kills enemies and earns currency to upgrade the Proxy<br></li><li> Different maps and modes for different play styles</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle enemies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939630/extras/29193850e05786e7526ff1dcd412a78a.poster.avif?t=1741582473\" width=376 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939630/extras/29193850e05786e7526ff1dcd412a78a.webm?t=1741582473\" type=\"